<!-- ══ HOMEWORK HELPER ══ -->
<div id="page-helper" class="page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <h2>Homework Helper</h2>
      <p id="helper-sub">Ask any question — I'll explain it step by step for your grade level.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Learning Mode Banner -->
    <div id="lm-banner" style="display:none;background:var(--yellow);border-radius:14px;padding:13px 18px;margin-bottom:16px;display:none;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-weight:800;color:#78350F;font-size:.88rem">
      🔒 <span>Learning Mode is ON — you'll need to attempt the answer before seeing the explanation.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="helper-grid">
      <!-- Input -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">✏️ Your Question</div>
        <div class="subject-row" id="subj-row">
          <button class="sub-btn sel" onclick="selSubj('Math',this)">➕ Math</button>
          <button class="sub-btn" onclick="selSubj('Grammar',this)">✏️ Grammar</button>
          <button class="sub-btn" onclick="selSubj('Science',this)">🔬 Science</button>
          <button class="sub-btn" onclick="selSubj('History',this)">🌍 History</button>
          <button class="sub-btn" onclick="selSubj('Other',this)">💬 Other</button>
        </div>
        <textarea id="q-input" placeholder="Type your homework question here...

Examples:
• Average of: 11, 12, 11, 12 inches
• Solve for x: 3x + 7 = 22
• What caused World War I?
• Explain mitosis vs meiosis

Ctrl+Enter to submit"></textarea>
        <button class="solve-btn" id="solve-btn" onclick="solveQ()">🚀 Explain it to me</button>
      </div>

      <!-- Output -->
      <div class="card" style="overflow-y:auto;max-height:660px">
        <div class="card-title">💡 Step-by-Step Explanation</div>

        <div id="empty-st" style="text-align:center;padding:36px 0;color:var(--muted)">
          <div style="font-size:2.6rem;margin-bottom:8px">🤔</div>
          <p style="font-weight:700">Enter your question and I'll walk you through it!</p>
        </div>
        <div id="load-st" style="display:none"><div class="loading"><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><div class="dot"></div><span>Thinking...</span></div></div>
        <div id="err-st" style="display:none"><div class="error-box" id="err-msg"></div></div>

        <!-- Learning Mode attempt box -->
        <div id="attempt-box" style="display:none">
          <div class="attempt-box">
            <h3>🔒 Try it yourself first!</h3>
            <p>Before I show you the explanation, give it a shot. What do you think the answer might be? There's no penalty — just try!</p>
            <input class="attempt-input" id="attempt-input" placeholder="Your attempt..." />
            <button class="attempt-submit" onclick="submitAttempt()">Submit my attempt →</button>
            <button class="attempt-skip" onclick="skipAttempt()">I really don't know, show me</button>
