        </div>

        <div class="answer-area" id="ans-area">
          <div id="ans-content"></div>
          <div id="ans-locked" class="answer-locked" style="display:none">
            🔒 Answer hidden — complete the quiz above to reveal it, or ask your teacher to unlock.
            <br><button class="unlock-btn" onclick="unlockAnswer()">Unlock Answer</button>
          </div>
          <div id="vid-links" style="display:none">
            <div class="vid-links">
              <div class="vid-links-title">🎥 Related Videos on YouTube</div>
              <div id="vid-links-list"></div>
            </div>
